  "description": "A wide-angle shot captures a majestic bridge stretching across a deep blue body of water. The bridge is a suspension type, featuring prominent towers and a network of cables supporting the roadway. Several vehicles are visible traversing the bridge. In the background, rolling hills covered with lush greenery rise dramatically, adding depth to the scene. A distant cityscape is nestled along the shoreline, and a few boats dot the water. The sky is clear and blue, creating a bright and airy atmosphere.",
